      <h1 class='title'>Equity Loans Scheme</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 cc108-9WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_108ws' title='Col. 108WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c108WS' name='column_108ws' href='#column_108ws' rel='bookmark'>108WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05263'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_552'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tim-loughton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_552' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tim Loughton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-tim-loughton" title="Mr Tim Loughton">Tim Loughton</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05263">To ask the Deputy Prime Minister how many social workers will benefit from interest-free mortgages under the equity loans scheme announced by his Department. [134835]</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_109ws' title='Col. 109WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c109WS' name='column_109ws' href='#column_109ws' rel='bookmark'>109WS</a>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05264'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_553'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-keith-hill' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_553' title='Link to this speech by Mr Keith Hill' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-keith-hill" title="Mr Keith Hill">Keith Hill</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05264">The balance of products taken up by individual key worker groups will depend on the severity of recruitment and retention problems in their sector, the level of employer contribution and the personal circumstances of individual key workers. Full details of the operation of the scheme will be announced by the beginning of March.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
